data.description: Ranch Style Home in Wonderful Westcliff! For almost 50 years, the owners have made a lifetime of memories in this home. Now is your chance to nestle down in this wonderful Fort Worth neighborhood, add your own personal touches and make a lifetime of memories of your own. With over 4,000 sq ft and just over a half an acre, this home features 3 bdrms, 3 baths, 2 dining areas plus an office & flex room with sliding wall divider (could be converted to 4th bdrm). The great room with vaulted ceilings and exposed wood beams, stacked stone fireplace with oversized hearth, is the focal point of the home without question. Addition features include full wet bar, wood worked ceilings, St. Charles steel kitchen cabinets, sunroom with water feature, private outdoor patio from the primary bedroom, addition storage rooms in garage, stacked stone exterior, pool with pool equipment and storage room. Office could make excellent game room or home gym. Lots of space in this fun and flexible floorplan!
